    {
      "id": "96",
      "name": "媒體",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "過場動畫與預告",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "2.4版本預告：「飛彩鐫流年」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/feab5d3627cfa529fc15798565055b7d_2580170926795710714.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2021年12月26日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "華彩難及之處，詭譎的敵影伺機而動。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "白晝永無之境，殘存的火種仍未平息。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "而在日光照耀的地方，人們依然滿懷期待。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "那些誠摯的希望，一如盛放的煙火，流光溢彩。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "2.5版本預告「薄櫻初綻時」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/f2db459e7cac76c8ee70779ec37e82c6_8366422823113481613.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年2月4日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "神櫻自古立於影向山頂，根系深盤地底，綿延不絕。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在它的蔭蔽之下，有人類誠心祈福，有妖狐笑看浮世，也有神明夢繫須臾永恆。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "世事流轉，人聚又散，唯有緋櫻連年爛漫，隨風而安。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "音樂",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "《佚落遷忘之島》",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/18116e44fd814cd2b83ac451d7af1f4d_8206199976173794975.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年4月13日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
